/KABe a Jew / Zayn a Yid/XX/PR
Being a Jew means running forever to God/PR
even if you are Godòs betrayer,/PR
means expecting to hear any day,/PR
even if you are a nay sayer,/PR
the blare of Messiahòs horn;/PR
/PR
means, even if you wish to,/PR
you cannot escape Godòs snares,/PR
you cannot cease to pray--/PR
even after all the prayers,/PR
even after all the "evens"./PR
Aaron Zeitlin (translated from the Yiddish by Robert Friend [adapted])/XX/PR
