/KAI Know Not Your Ways/XX/PR
I know not your ways--/PR
A sunset is for me/PR
a godset./PR
Where are you going,/PR
God?/PR
Take me along,/PR
if, in the "along,"/PR
it is light,/PR
God./PR
/PR
I am afraid of the dark./PR
Malka Heifetz Tussman (translated from the Yiddish by Marcia Falk)/XX/PR
